# Bluesky Topic Modeling Web App

This app uses LDA + t-SNE to analyze Bluesky posts, providing topic clusters and sentiment insights.

🌀 Built with Streamlit  
📊 Topic modeling: sklearn LDA  
😊 Sentiment: TextBlob  
📍 Visualization: Plotly

## Try it live:
Once deployed via Streamlit Cloud, anyone can interact with the analysis online.

1. pip install -r requirements.txt

2. python bluesky_lda_pipeline.py

3. streamlit run app.py
